Senior reporter Siphamandla Goge was in court for us. #DStv403 #eNCA  JOHANNESBURG - Former Mkhondo Local Municipality Mayor Vusi Motha has been arrested and has appeared in court. His co-accused Sifiso Sangweni faces a charge of providing a firearm and ammunition to a person not authorised to carry it. The case has been adjourned to 24 January. Both the accused were remanded in custody. Watch the video above for more details on this story. 